==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Morne
<hw>Morne</hw> <pr>(m⟦ocir⟧rn)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>morne</ets> sad, sorrowful. See <er>Mourn</er>.]</ety> <def>A ring
fitted upon the head of a lance to prevent wounding an adversary in
tilting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

